Description
    This toolkit provides a language as well as a few utility programs
    to generate random faked databases from a schema file written
    in a special language.

Installation
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    sudo make install

Usage
    cd ~/some-work-directory
    cht-compile /path/to/samples/sanity.cht
    cht-rows2sql data/*.rows.json

See the demo .cht file

    http://github.com/agentzh/cheater/blob/master/samples/sanity.cht

as well as the (declarative) test suite

    http://github.com/agentzh/cheater/blob/master/samples/sanity.cht

for more features and use cases.

